                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020113-30-off161 t18020113-30-cd162"></join>, a box, value 8d. sixty breeches balls, value 30s. and twelve rubbers, value 6s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18020113-30-victim377" type="victimName">
